Triceradon and his dinobots:Stegtron,Dinotron, and Ultracon, heard about a battle that just happened at the Maximal base. They felt guilty about not being there to help the Maximals. So the four of them took sentry posts just outside the Maximal base. They were ready to defend the base if it was attacked again.
